text:
Differential treatment. Was asked to order via QR code when at counter already, claiming short handed (when there are 3 staffs) but the next customer can order at counter.

The steamed Kaya bread didn’t come hot or warm. Can’t even tell whether it is steamed actually cos it is not soft.

French toast was not sold out even at 8.30am..

Glad that I can now enjoy local delights after my gyane appointment ! Many local options, personal favorite was laksa and mee siam and not forgetting soft boiled eggs and kaya butter toast. A variety of items were also suitable for my little ones. Staff were friendly as well.
Food is too oily especially for a maternity hospital.
Laksa pasta spaghetti wasn’t cooked. So many staff but food is bad.
Great place to chill indoors and outdoors, excellent service by all staff. A fan for both dine-in and takeaways.
